Description: Linux/Kali command explanation tool with dual perspectives
 A command-line tool designed for Kali Linux and Ubuntu that explains
 the meaning and usage of shell commands from two angles:
 .
  - General perspective (sysadmin / DevOps best practices)
  - Security perspective (pentesting / CTF / privilege escalation)
 .
 Supports OpenAI, DeepSeek, and local Ollama backends.
 Bilingual output: Chinese (zh) and English (en).

